  [2]: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-Boot-2.4-Release-Notes#spring-boot-gradle-plugin
  [3]: https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/2.3.12.RELEASE/gradle-plugin/reference/html/#packaging-executable-configuring-main-class
  [4]: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-Boot-2.0-Migration-Guide#configuration-updates
