The problem is in this block:

```java
    @Column(name = &quot;addresses&quot;)
    @OneToMany(mappedBy = &quot;client&quot;, cascade = CascadeType.ALL, fetch = FetchType.EAGER)
    private List&lt;AddressDataSet&gt; addresses = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
